            <h1 class="text-[32px] font-serif mb-2" style="color: #FFFFFF;">《望庐山瀑布》</h1>
            <p class="text-[14px] mb-10" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">唐 · 李白</p>

            <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
                <p class="text-[22px] font-serif leading-loose" style="color: #FFFFFF;"><span style="color: #FCD34D;">日照</span>香炉生<span style="color: #93C5FD;">紫烟</span>，</p>
                <p class="text-[22px] font-serif leading-loose" style="color: #FFFFFF;">遥看瀑布<span style="color: #86EFAC;">挂前川</span>。</p>
                <p class="text-[22px] font-serif leading-loose" style="color: #FFFFFF;"><span style="color: #FCA5A5;">飞流</span>直下<span style="color: #FBBF24;">三千尺</span>，</p>
                <p class="text-[22px] font-serif leading-loose" style="color: #FFFFFF;">疑是<span style="color: #C4B5FD;">银河</span>落九天。</p>
